snippet.title: Bigg Boss Triumph : @ElvishYadavVlogs's Comic Chronicles!
snippet.description:
Step into the captivating world of a true entertainer, Elvish Yadav ‚Äì a well-known Indian Youtuber and winner of Bigg Boss OTT Season 2 . This podcast is your express ticket to Elvish's journey, from his YouTube adventures to the thrill of winning Bigg Boss OTT, all while cherishing the unique connection with his supportive fanbase. It's a brief yet lively chat, giving you a glimpse into the life of a vibrant personality, filled with stories, achievements, and the warmth of a dedicated community. Tune in for a dose of entertainment and insights into the dynamic world of Elvish Yadav!

snippet.title: 100 Million - DIVINE, Karan Aujla | Official Music Video
snippet.description:
Download & Stream: https://lnk.to/100M

'100 Million' is an ode to the unparalleled success achieved by DIVINE and Karan Aujla. This track not only celebrates their achievements but also stands as an anthem, for those with grand dreams. As they savour the fruits of their labour, the artists reflect on the enduring habits that propelled them to the pinnacle. Fueled by explosive bars and bravado, this track marks the inception of a collaborative project between the two industry titans.

Audio Credits:

Music Production: Trox, Samarei

Synopsis:
Militant activities are going out of control in the Srinagar Valley, so a new and elite unit, Air Dragons, is commissioned by the Air Headquarters. They are now the first responders to any hostile activity. They comprise of the best combat aviators handpicked from across the IAF. FIGHTER is the story of Air Dragons who are willing to give it their all for the nation while going through the highs and lows of their internal and external battles.

snippet.description:

Presenting the first single "Choodu Nanna" from 'Yatra 2' starring Mammootty, Jiiva & others. Directed by Mahi V Raghav, Music Composed by Santhosh Narayanan.

Song Credits:-
Lyrics : Bhaskarabhatla Ravi Kumar
Singers : Vijaynarain
Composed, Arranged and Programmed by Santhosh Narayanan
Additional Vocals : Santhosh Narayanan
Recorded by Santhosh Narayanan, Rupendar Venkatesh
Recorded at Future Tense Studios -  Chennai
Recording Engineer : Rupendar Venkatesh
Studio Assist : Jaba Raj
Mixed and Mastered by Santhosh Narayanan at Future Tense Studios
Musicians Coordinator : Meenakshi Santhosh

Movie Credits:-
Written & Directed by: Mahi V Raghav
Producer: Shiva Meka
Banners: Three Autumn Leaves, V Celluloid
Music Director: Santhosh Narayanan
DOP : Madhie
Editor : Shravan Katikaneni
Art Director: Selva Kumar
Cast :
Mammootty, Jiiva, Ketaki Narayan, Suzanne Bernert, Mahesh Manjrekar

Lyrics:-
Pallavi:
Choodu Naannaa...Choosthunnaavaa naannaa.. Needa leni nena veella dheema
yemitii enthatiii premaa.. 
Naa dhareto thochakunte 
 Nii vembadae memu antuu
Kadilaaru ento aa nammakam
Nenelaa odduku  cheradam...  Veellanelaa  odduku cherchadam

Charanam 1:
Inti peddhaa.. Kanumoosthey ainavaallu anadhale kadha. 
Nuvvu lekaa.. Prathi ooruu ooruu anadha avvadam yendayyaa..
  Nuvvu lekaa..... Nuvvu lekaa..... Nuvvu lekaa...
Idhi yenaaduu.. Jarigundadhayyaa.. Oo pedayya.. 
Indhari kannulu chimme kanniitinanthaa..
Thudavaalani vundhi kodukuga
Anduku avasaramaiyyee kondantha dhairyam naakivvu..

Charanam 2:
enthala abhimaaname kuripisthunnaro ee janam Anduke ee janmalo teerchesukuntaa ee runam Gadapaki prathi gadapaki nenavuthaa raksha thoranam  Maatapai untaanani chesthunnaa tholi santhakam
Needa leni nena veella dheema...
Choodu naannaa.. Choodu naannaa..
 Choodu naannaa.. Choodu naannaa..
 Choodu naannaa.. Choodu naannaa..
     Choodu naannaa.. Choodu naannaa..

snippet.title: VEG THALI | 15 Varieties of Veg Recipes | Huge South Indian Veg Thali Recipes Cooking In Village
snippet.description:
Today, in our village, we cook 15 varieties of vegetarian recipes for the special Tamil day of the Pongal festival. We cook South Indian Veg thali recipes by cooking the following recipes: Rice, Sambar, Rasam, Mor, Payasam, Appalam, Vadai, Sweet Pongal, Potato fry, Lady Finger masala, Brinjal Masial, Raw banana Fry, Cabbage, Thandu Keerai Masiyal, and Pickle.

The taste is savory!

snippet.title: Exclusive Look Of The Newly Built Ram Mandir & Ayodhya Airport | I Love My India | Curly Tales
snippet.description:
Curly Tales has exclusive access to the newly built Ram Mandir &  Maharishi Valmiki Airport just before the launch. 
The Ram Mandir, set to be inaugurated on January 22nd, has preparations going on in full swing as around 4000 laborers are working on it around the clock. 
The temple is a testament to architectural marvel, constructed without the use of metal or concrete. Instead, a special rock imported from the Bansi Mountain in Rajasthan has been employed.
Along with that get a glimpse of Ayodhya‚Äôs four transformed lanes which are the - Bhaktipath, Janma Bhoomi Path, Ram Path & Dharma Path which are reconstructed on the basis of 4 vedas. 
You will also be amazed to see a new systematic way of Darshan for better crowd management that has been arranged by the government. 
Additionally, we give you an exclusive look at the Maharishi Valmiki International Airport, set to launch soon after being constructed in a record time of just 20 months. Inspired by the new Ram Mandir, the airport's walls are adorned with paintings depicting stories from the Ramayana. With the capacity to host about 10 lakh passengers annually, this airport is a remarkable addition to Ayodhya's infrastructure. 
So what are you waiting for,  book your tickets now as various modes of transportation have now been made available to visit Ram Lala.    

#ayodhya #rammandirayodhya #curlytales #foodandtravel #ayodhyadham #ayodhyarammandir #ayodhyatemple #rammandir

Zimbabwe won the toss and decided to bowl first in the 2nd T20I. Sri Lanka lost their top three batters for one-digit scores but later Charith Asalanka and Angelo Mathews stitched up a brilliant partnership. Sri Lanka ended with a total of 173 runs and Zimbabwe then came into bat. Opener Craig Ervine played a superb knock worth 70 runs while Luke Jongwe and Clive Madande's heroics ultimately took Zimbabwe to a thrilling four-wicket victory.

snippet.title: Shri Ram Lalla | Sonu Nigam | Ram Bhajan | Amitabh S Verma | Mukul Varma | Ram Mandir Song
snippet.description:
Get ready to feel the joy! "Shri Ram Lalla" song in Sonu Nigam's voice is all about the happiness of Lord Ram coming back to #Ayodhya. This special song is like a musical hug for everyone excited for #RamMandir.

The beautiful city of #Ayodhya is getting ready for a big celebration, and this song captures that wonderful feeling.

Singer - Sonu Nigam

About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal‚Äôs Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal‚Äôs Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

snippet.title: Main ATAL Hoon (Trailer 2) | Pankaj Tripathi | Ravi Jadhav | Vinod Bhanushali | 19 Jan 2024
snippet.description:
More than a poet. More than a statesman. More than a Prime Minister. Presenting trailer 2 of #MainATALHoon. 

Vinod Bhanushali presents, Main ATAL Hoon, a film on the extraordinary life of the leader you knew but the man you didn't, starring National Award winner Pankaj Tripathi. 

Directed by National Awardee Ravi Jadhav, and written by Rishi Virmani and Ravi Jadhav, "Main ATAL Hoon" produced by Bhanushali Studios Limited and Legend Studios, is produced by Vinod Bhanushali, Sandeep Singh, and Kamlesh Bhanushali.

The film releases on 19th January 2024 in cinemas near you.
